<br>
The time lmimit was a sugestion given to me by some comrads in Dal Kingdom, The druid Meucci has shown me that the warning thet poeple get that they are not welcome in our forest is when they come back for a cold, deed corpse.<br>
<br>
/ooc besides PvP deaths result in NO Exp loss or iteam loss right?  SO what are all these people crying asbout SHEESH!<br>
<br>
IC:  I do however salute your ideals and am currently considering leaving the Dal Kingdom, if some ACTION is not taken.  I am a warrior, the time for talk is over, we need to defend our lands and show the World that we are elves and we are NOT a joke<br>
<br>
/ooc besides in other games like D&amp;D non-elbves get maybe 40feet from the elven forst before they are shot.  In Magic the Gathering i belive its &quot;One bone broken for every branch snaped underfoot.  Elven Penalty for Tresspassin'&quot;  Should we everquest elves be any different... I think NOT!<br>
<br>
IC:  Well my friends i have to get back on the feild of battle!  I shall see you in Kelethin soon i hope.<br>
<br>
